Real World Use Cases
MySQL StatefulSet    → EBS (each pod own volume, same AZ)
Jenkins Master       → EBS (single pod, persistent home)
Shared uploads       → EFS (all webapp pods share files)
ML Model files       → EFS (all inference pods read same model)
Logs aggregation     → EFS (multiple pods write logs)
Config files         → EFS (all pods read same config)

